HelloMinecraft

Author(s):
smickles (xiberphim ,ot, gmail) a.k.a. Michael Carver

HelloMinecraft is a plugin for CraftBukkit (http://bukkit.org/) which is intended to broadcast
a customizable message to online players at regular (and also customizable) intervals.

As of this writing, HelloMinecraft is in early development and is considerably incomplete. 

Last Modified 23May11 by smickles